{"tid":2283490,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"14歲老貓有腎病可以點","createTime":"2020-11-12T15:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T11:07:48.000Z","uid":176705,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d23dd57078e58a32f6c9571c83d2b9feed5ed65d","tid":2283490,"uid":176705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T15:18:43.000Z","msg":"佢唔飲又唔食<br />\n用針筒餵佢食佢又會嘔出黎<br />\n宜家佢瘦到得排骨<br />\n行路冇咩力<br />\n平時唔摸得嘅地方宜家狂摸都冇反應<br />\n啊媽話係時候送佢去彩虹橋<br />\n但係我真係好唔捨得<br />\n大大話話養左13年<br />\n係咪真係冇曬辦法"},{"pid":"4036ff6b6d4cce08e67daac3f9f4a2f602bfe6d9","tid":2283490,"uid":193196,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T15:21:27.000Z","msg":"坦白講，你俾佢去啦"},{"pid":"dad63c88140a94a2620199eeffc5148a300a4cd6","tid":2283490,"uid":381575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T15:22:18.000Z","msg":"多D陪佢傾計，行埋最後一程啦"},{"pid":"cf18628a38ab2bad963a9465e10586f249c0f5b7","tid":2283490,"uid":176705,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T15:32:20.000Z","msg":"我都想好好咁送佢走<br />\n但係真係好唔捨得<br />\n明明上個月仲好精神<br />\n今個月就變成咁<br />\n佢由我小學陪到我出黎做野<br />\n我真係好想好想佢繼續陪我行落去<br />\n聽日啊媽就打去愛協book時間打針俾佢走<br />\n我真係冇辦法好好咁放手"},{"pid":"d5c67e70d906545a3c421442b1b95972287bf162","tid":2283490,"uid":239969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T16:17:53.000Z","msg":"絲打加油 我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6382b9b248d4955a8c6fd88b9e743a6f6db932","tid":2283490,"uid":239969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T16:18:23.000Z","msg":"會唔會上啲貓谷求助下 可能有人有好方法"},{"pid":"d93f14561ebfed747dd8b9146520510775f9d642","tid":2283490,"uid":176705,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d6382b9b248d4955a8c6fd88b9e743a6f6db932","tid":2283490,"uid":239969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T16:18:23.000Z","msg":"會唔會上啲貓谷求助下 可能有人有好方法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T16:21:34.000Z","msg":"屋企人已經決定左要俾佢走<br />\n我阻止都冇用，啊媽話想係佢冇咁辛苦個陣放手"},{"pid":"bcba5af744b57c345baaf18b44e425f43f07eaff","tid":2283490,"uid":239969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d93f14561ebfed747dd8b9146520510775f9d642","tid":2283490,"uid":176705,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d6382b9b248d4955a8c6fd88b9e743a6f6db932","tid":2283490,"uid":239969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T16:18:23.000Z","msg":"會唔會上啲貓谷求助下 可能有人有好方法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T16:21:34.000Z","msg":"屋企人已經決定左要俾佢走<br />\n我阻止都冇用，啊媽話想係佢冇咁辛苦個陣放手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T16:47:22.000Z","msg":"好心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da63d18ea52a360e19f2f1839df47c16ea6d037a","tid":2283490,"uid":222904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T17:09:20.000Z","msg":"我隻貓早幾個月同樣情況<br />\n持續左幾個星期就走咗<br />\n剩返嘅時間對佢好啲多啲陪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457f4621fef2ce4167feac77195a801a6640762a","tid":2283490,"uid":176705,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"已經卜左聽日去愛協俾佢走<br />\n仲要係我一個人帶佢去<br />\n心好痛<br />\n十三年真係好長<br />\n長到我以爲佢可以陪我一世"},{"pid":"2f837077e644ef57e32fe7080953cf3c550ecb38","tid":2283490,"uid":273157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:00:40.000Z","msg":"撐住，其實一世都好短，轉眼間就可以天堂再會"},{"pid":"67d3b787dec14e0856f678a54e5526119f4631c8","tid":2283490,"uid":273157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:01:12.000Z","msg":"比佢好好咁離開比較好，希望再無痛苦"},{"pid":"f28274d7921b168988b076f3662eec6d07f117ca","tid":2283490,"uid":5339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:36:55.000Z","msg":"Take care"},{"pid":"9dd308a46f58ea37e0087840475ddeed4b6670a1","tid":2283490,"uid":369450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:40:36.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我隻貓貓幾個月前都係腎病走左"},{